town in the southern province of Maguindanao, while aboard a mini
bus.
</P>
<P>
The victim, who was on his way to work, was fired upon by two
gunmen who reportedly boarded the same bus.
</P>
<P>
Police investigators are still trying to determine whether or
not the reporter's death was related to his profession. 
