<HEADLINE> Cheapper Access to Industrial Parks Offerred in </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
KAMPALA, April 18 (Xinhua) -- Ugandan young enterpreneurs will
get cheapper access to industrial parks, local newspaper ''The
New Vision'' reported Saturday.
</P>
<P>
The Private Sector Development Program (PSDP) has decided to
set up industrial parks which will provide with industrial lease
at a small fees to young enterprenuers, said Billy Butamanya, the
coordinator of business skill development program.
