<TEXT>
<P>
TIANJIN, April 18 (Xinhua) -- A delegation from the government
of Thailand, led by Thai Deputy Prime Minister Supachai
Panitchpakdi, visited the port city of Tianjin in north China
today.
</P>
<P>
