Statistics show that Thailand had opened 87 joint ventures in
Tianjin by the end of March, with a total contracted value
standing at 120 million US dollars. These projects cover
wide-ranging areas, including industry, agriculture, real estate,
transportation and international trade.
</P>
<P>
Tianjin's 1997 export volume to Thailand reached 27.4 million
US dollars, with the January-March figure for this year standing
at 6.6 million US dollars.
</P>
<P>
The Thai delegation left here for Beijing this afternoon.
</P>
</TEXT>
</BODY>
