Yemeni President Ali Abdullah Saleh to his Djibouti counterpart
Hassan Gouled Aptidon.
</P>
<P>
The message will deal with ways of promoting the bilateral ties
as well as regional and international issues, he said.
</P>
<P>
He expressed pleasure that both Yemen and Djibouti are willing
to promote the relations for their common interests. 
