<HEADLINE> CCPIT Develops Rapidly </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, April 18 (Xinhua) -- The past few years have witnessed
a rapid growth of the China Council for Promotion of International
Trade (CCPIT).
</P>
<P>
By now, it has set up 48 regional and 652 county-level
branches, as well as 17 industrial councils such as those of
machinery, electronics, light industry, textiles and grain.
</P>
<P>
CCPIT, China's sole nationwide non-governmental trade
promotion organization, now has 70,000 member enterprises. 
</P>
