<HEADLINE> World Cup Tickets Sold on Telephone </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
PARIS, April 17 (Xinhua) -- The remaining 110,000 World Cup
tickets will be available on telephone from April 22, the French
World Cup Organization Committee announced here on Friday.
</P>
<P>
The soccer fans in 18 European countries will have one last
chance to go to France for the biggest soccer event this summer as
the French organizers decided to open three hotlines next
Wednesday from 8 a.m. to 8 p.m.(all local time).
</P>
