</P>
<P>
 "People's Daily"
</P>
<P>
-- China will do its best to help Thailand overcome its present
difficulties, Premier Zhu Rongji said Friday when meeting with
Thailand's Vice Prime Minister Supachai Panitchpakdi.
</P>
<P>
-- The Chinese People's Liberation Army (PLA) and the armed
police have launched an education focusing on sacrificing their
private interests to the overall situation and supporting reforms
among officers and soldiers, and have achieved progress with the
formation of a healthy atmosphere featuring sacrificial spirit,
discipline-abiding and responsibility-awareness.
</P>
<P>
-- The People's Bank of China (PBOC) announced Friday that three
